data.description: NEW CONSTRUCTION! To be built by premier builder Stonebridge Homes on the PRIME LOT in the community. The Essex features 4 bedrooms and 3 baths. The first floor features a wide open floor plan with soaring cathedral ceilings in the living room. One bedroom is conveniently located on the first floor adjacent to a full bath, perfect for a guest suite or home office. The second floor primary suite is huge with a sitting room and walk-in closet. Enjoy the convenience of 2nd floor laundry. This model also features a covered wrap-around front porch, two car garage, and a full walk-out basement ready to be finished. Tons of upgrade options will allow you to customize and turn this into your dream home! The future of Union Point is bright! Get in now and watch this neighborhood transform into a vibrant Live, Work, Play community! Acres of open space; miles of trails; playground; dog parks; on-site Commuter Rail.  TO BE BUILT ON LOT # 1.
